{"tid":879291,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦不知名問題求救⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-10-27T19:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:00:59.000Z","uid":22735,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b429ec2344bb0a3d9ae399a19fbbd133c2fb69f8","tid":879291,"uid":22735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:35:14.000Z","msg":"事源係部電腦係正常上網睇片完全冇問題，但係就一玩遊戲就會出現突然畫面卡死，然後等半分鐘左右就會自動彈出桌面⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先我就懷疑係系統有驅動撞左，搞左一輪又修復又重裝driver都搞唔掂，然後就連系統都重裝埋，都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁唔係軟件問題唯有試硬件，分別用aida64，furmark等等都完全冇問題⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n神奇嘅地方在於玩Farcry5就定時一分半鐘內出事，PUBG就不定時出事，NBA2K19就完全唔會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跪求大神出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附帶電腦list<br />\n8700k<br />\nASUS M10F<br />\n16GB DDR4 3600"},{"pid":"90a527f718e2d68a79cf09c7e7d32740ce9ab09a","tid":879291,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:36:15.000Z","msg":"拎出去去整"},{"pid":"73e02339a517391ebcbe82b21c4ea3764364265f","tid":879291,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"零晨三點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDel左個防毒試下"},{"pid":"50ed584ed01e1126b9a1799473b5364aeead0d39","tid":879291,"uid":22735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e02339a517391ebcbe82b21c4ea3764364265f","tid":879291,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"零晨三點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDel左個防毒試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:43:54.0